I want to make a discord bot with a few key capabilities:
Key features:
- Slippi Lookup: I give it a Slippi.gg connect code and it returns their rank info
- Price History Lookup: I give it an amazon url and it returns amazon price history from somewhere lkike camel camel camel
- Tracker.gg Monitor: in the backend it keeps a list of riot ids to track and it periodically checks tracker.gg for new games; once a new game is detected, it messages in the discord channel (or notifies however else)
- VoiceMemo Transcription: I want to be able to upload a voice memo in mp4 format and it transcribes it using (preferably using offline model)